 make a significant contribution to our understanding of this period in American history1 fThis work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-No Derivativesuhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nd/4.0  aDescription based on information from the publisher. 0aStamp collectingzUnited StatesxHistory. 0aPostage stampszUnited StatesxHistory. 4aElectronic books.2 aMichigan Publishing (University of Michigan)epublisher.1 iSupplement (work):aBrennan, SheilatStamping American memoryh1 online resource (50 photos) 0aDigital humanities (Ann Arbor, Mich.)40zAccess to the Michigan Publishing online version:uhttps://doi.org/10.3998/mpub.9847183